This mod have very interactive functionality which encourage the visitor to participate in all activities of the site.
Features -
*********
1- Admin can assign points(reward points) to site-user on his/her(site-user) activities.
  i.e-
      on login
      on blogging
      on files upload
      on video upload
      on discussion topics
      on bookmarks
      on order
      on store
      All the active plugins will be automatically adds in above list.

2- Site-user will have option to redeem their reward points against site-offer

3-Admin can publish site offer as coupon and decide the value of coupon in terms of poins(reward points).

4-Admin will also have the option to create coupon against points or cash even as well as both points and cash


